channel.title: Gathering interest to participate in the consumption and usage of a project
channel.description:
Hello, my name is ranger squad and I am here today to gather a general idea of the amount of interest of the community to participate in the usage of a project,
Would anyone be interested in playing a "fun server" (like funscap3 or Allstar) if I was to create one?
Yours sincerely, Ranger Squad
